      • delete

          java.lang.String dataStreamId,

        Parameters:
        feedId - the id of the parent of the datastream that holds the datapoint
        dataStreamId - the id of the parent of the datapoint

      • deleteMultiple

        void deleteMultiple(int feedId,

                  java.lang.String startAt)
                    throws HttpException
        Parameters:
        feedId - the id of the parent of the datastream that holds the datapoints
        dataStreamId - the id of the parent of the datapoints
        startAt - any datapoints starting from this date, inclusive will be deleted over the API
        Throws:
        HttpException - if failed to delete the datapoints over the API
